e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebfe79c3bf9cabbe882cbcc8df56ea78f69d043","tid":1784702,"uid":334861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72745f4def2273c1eff19272e5b7c66860f2b681","tid":1784702,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"而家毅進先係名校"},{"pid":"69bdbf3cda79f84c849e0ad891c3e36ceaa4c1b3","tid":1784702,"uid":162492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd1fe3209155a1752602e2564eb640f779e5c17","tid":1784702,"uid":3776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"見到母校上榜<br />\n都唔知開心定傷心<br />\n開心既係間學校開始染紅 但學生仲分到是非<br />\n傷心既係你地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}